Hi,

 

Sandeep has asked to have a weekly strategy meeting around Subscription after discussing what’s next in our UAC Growth meeting this morning.

So I’m transforming the UAC meeting into this Strategy meeting, adding a few other key stakeholders, and moving to 1 hour at 11:00.

 

Some immediate topics for discussion that arose:

  • Concerns that we don’t have a product market fit between our “Maude’s” and the product offering we put into the market
  • Review strategy and product roadmap as relates to the above concerns
  • Review the underlying assumptions of our revenue projection model
  • Review Marketing/Ad strategy, our spend/month, and is this missing from our projection model

 

Thanks,

Louis
